
tar:
 run plasma-update-versions (ensure it is using the right branches)
 set ORIGIN=trunk or stable in ./plasma
 run ./plasma script to make tars
 tell sysadmins to make tars available to packagers
 tell release-team@kde.org, plasma-devel@kde.org

branch:
 on a new 5.x release make branches Plasma/5.x:
  run branchme
  ensure translations are switched to correct branch in projects.kde.org

prepare:
 www/announcements/plasma-5.x.y.php
 www/info/plasma-5.x.y.php
 Dot story
 tell sysadmins to free the source

tag pre-launch:
 tag by running tagme
 branch plasma-workspace-wallpapers
 first make 5.1 directory then..
 svn copy svn+ssh://svn@svn.kde.org/home/kde/trunk/KDE/plasma-workspace-wallpapers/ svn+ssh://svn@svn.kde.org/home/kde/branches/plasma/5.1/plasma-workspace-wallpapers/ -m "branch for 5.1"

 tag plasma-workspace-wallpapers
 svn copy svn+ssh://svn@svn.kde.org/home/kde/trunk/KDE/plasma-workspace-wallpapers/ svn+ssh://svn@svn.kde.org/home/kde/tags/plasma-workspace-wallpapers/4.98.0 -m "Tagging 4.98.0 Plasma 5.0 RC"

launch:
 www/announcements/index.php
 www/announcements/release_data.php
 www/index.php
 publish Dot story on front page
 e-mail kde-announce@kde.org
 update bugzilla version numbers

